cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO

This paper is about object detection in videos using deep neural networks. The most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as the paper deals with image and video analysis. The second likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning) as deep neural networks are used for object detection. The third likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as the paper deals with intelligent systems that can detect objects in videos. The fourth likely category is cs.MM (Multimedia) as the paper deals with video analysis. The fifth likely category is cs.RO (Robotics) as object detection is an important task in robotics.
